WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:02.107
Hey, good morning everybody.

00:00:02.107 --> 00:00:04.200
How are y'all doing today?

00:00:04.586 --> 00:00:09.339
I'm Brandon Biggs and this is Diana Biggs, and we're excited to be with you all today.

00:00:09.339 --> 00:00:11.931
We have some things on our heart we're going to pray about.

00:00:12.456 --> 00:00:14.880
Remember the conference with Billy Brim?

00:00:14.880 --> 00:00:18.479
It's coming in February.

00:00:19.199 --> 00:00:26.480
Rick Renner and Billy Brim are going to do end times eschatology teachings.

00:00:29.173 --> 00:00:36.600
He is an expert in the Greek and she has been around for a long time learning about the end times.

00:00:36.600 --> 00:00:50.540
She's an expert in knowing the Bible and where we are with the end times—not being flaky, just straight-up Word of God, and I love that about them.

00:00:50.830 --> 00:00:53.520
I'm excited about it.

00:00:54.053 --> 00:01:01.839
It's a couple of months away, through November, December, and January, but it gives you enough time to pray about if you're supposed to be there.

00:01:01.839 --> 00:01:12.159
What a way to start the year off, getting yourself immersed in the Word of God and getting yourself ready for 2025.

00:01:12.159 --> 00:01:20.240
I believe we are going to see some major things in 2025, ladies and gentlemen—a great acceleration.

00:01:23.760 --> 00:01:36.047
Talking to you about that great acceleration, I warned you about New Orleans and I saw a one-man shooter, and that happened yesterday.

00:01:36.047 --> 00:01:39.386
My condolences to the families; we grieve with you.

00:01:39.679 --> 00:01:45.324
If you watch our YouTube channel, we pray for you.

00:01:45.324 --> 00:01:54.799
We know the loss of someone in your family is hard, and I pray for peace for your heart in this time of grieving.

00:01:57.013 --> 00:02:07.580
When I get a word from the Lord warning to pray for something, there are a lot of you that question if this guy is flaky or not.

00:02:07.580 --> 00:02:25.000
Now, I'm not trying to toot my own horn, folks, but I take it very seriously.

00:02:26.350 --> 00:03:00.720
I don't come on here just to waste my time; I come on here because the Lord has told me specifically, 'Brandon, I need you to sound the alarm and be a watchman for Me in these last days.

00:03:00.720 --> 00:03:31.120
' Whenever I come here and tell you there's an attack coming on New Orleans, we have to take it more seriously.

00:03:31.120 --> 00:03:48.896
It is a rebuke to me because I only prayed over it one time.

00:03:48.896 --> 00:04:01.954
We were interceding for it like we did for the presidency.

00:04:01.954 --> 00:04:18.100
When the Lord gives me an assignment, He showed me Nashville and Las Vegas.

00:04:18.100 --> 00:04:33.280
He said there are more cities, but He won't give those until later.

00:04:33.280 --> 00:04:50.580
The Lord showed me these three cities specifically; it wasn't Atlanta or New York.

00:04:50.580 --> 00:05:00.080
He said New Orleans, Nashville, and Las Vegas.

00:05:12.205 --> 00:05:14.729
The thing in Nashville happened—I think we averted it.

00:05:14.729 --> 00:05:28.159
It wasn't a shooting incident; it was a drone thing.

00:05:28.159 --> 00:05:54.070
I've been praying over these drones all the time, as they've been on my heart—strapping things to these devices and trying to cause mass destruction.

00:06:07.166 --> 00:06:10.183
The Lord already warned us; this is part of what I've been seeing.

00:06:10.183 --> 00:06:17.269
Well, that man was busted by the FBI.

00:06:17.269 --> 00:06:20.053
Glory to God!

00:06:20.053 --> 00:06:25.759
Then we have this man down there.

00:06:25.759 --> 00:06:49.680
When I was looking into the New Orleans thing, I saw that it was a one-person thing.

00:06:49.680 --> 00:07:15.039
Well, that happened; nine to eleven people were shot, and I think two people passed away, which is terrible.

00:07:15.039 --> 00:07:47.200
Now the next target I'm praying over is Las Vegas, specifically the Strip, praying that all the people there will not come into any harm's way.

00:07:47.200 --> 00:07:52.080
These are serious times, folks.

00:07:52.080 --> 00:08:05.879
When the Lord gives a word, it's not like we're just here to be entertained.

00:08:05.879 --> 00:08:44.480
I'm here to tell you what's coming, as the Lord has put me as a watchman on the wall, yelling out from a distance, 'Look, look, we must pray!

00:08:44.480 --> 00:09:10.496
' He said to raise up a million-person prayer army that will pray with you every single day.

00:09:14.434 --> 00:09:19.180
I believe we are on our way.

00:09:19.180 --> 00:09:36.360
We have about 40,000 people come and pray, and that's just the beginning.

00:09:36.360 --> 00:10:07.610
I believe this is going to grow and grow, and we are going to have results.

00:10:16.799 --> 00:10:16.959
People say, 'Well, you called that out and we didn't see anything.

00:10:16.959 --> 00:10:19.510
' Praise God!

00:10:19.510 --> 00:10:25.828
That's what we want to happen.

00:10:25.828 --> 00:11:06.267
This is fruit from what the Lord is showing me, but we don't want to see our prayer fail; we want to see prayer success, which is peace and safety, and no weapon formed against these people prospering.

00:11:06.267 --> 00:11:14.992
Now we have a tragedy that happened, and it's terrible.

00:11:14.992 --> 00:11:33.154
Maybe we averted more; there could have been a bigger event or we could have delayed it.

00:11:41.600 --> 00:11:50.320
I don't want to see the wicked be successful in any plot or plan they have against people.

00:11:50.320 --> 00:12:10.731
We still don't have full election results; it's been going on for two weeks.

00:12:10.731 --> 00:12:17.600
They still haven't called the House completely.

00:12:26.720 --> 00:12:34.320
I told you corruption would be there and things would try to be delayed.

00:12:34.320 --> 00:12:49.960
Let's take communion and pray together, believing God that we have authority.

00:12:49.960 --> 00:13:05.229
We thank You, Father, that by Your stripes we are healed.

00:13:05.229 --> 00:13:16.423
You were wounded for our transgressions and bruised for our iniquities.

00:13:20.400 --> 00:13:35.067
The chastisement of our peace was upon You, and with Your stripes, we are healed physically, mentally, emotionally, and financially.

00:13:43.390 --> 00:13:46.284
We thank You for that Shalom, that peace that passes understanding.

00:13:46.284 --> 00:14:10.080
If Your Word abides in us, we shall ask what we will and it shall be done.

00:14:11.039 --> 00:14:31.200
We stand on the Word of God today and believe we receive deliverance in the name of Jesus over our bodies.

00:14:32.480 --> 00:15:19.599
We apply the blood of Jesus over Diana, from the top of her head to the soles of her feet, and over my children, our finances, our house, our car, and our jobs.

00:15:19.599 --> 00:15:46.525
According to Deuteronomy 28, we are blessed in the city and in the field, coming in and going out.

00:15:46.525 --> 00:16:09.259
Thank You, Lord, that we walk in divine health and have supernatural wisdom.

00:16:09.880 --> 00:16:32.459
I thank You for creative ideas to get wealth and that everything we put our hands to would prosper.

00:16:36.365 --> 00:16:44.440
We take authority over any kind of confusion.

00:16:44.440 --> 00:17:13.039
As it says in 2 Timothy 1:7, God has not given us a spirit of fear but of power, and of love, and of a well-balanced mind.

00:17:20.149 --> 00:17:33.440
I thank You for mental clarity and focus so that we hear You and will not follow a stranger's voice.

00:17:44.800 --> 00:17:53.039
There are a lot of people here from different backgrounds—Catholic, Methodist, LDS—from all over the world.

00:18:02.850 --> 00:18:18.933
You may not always agree with how I take communion, but my heart is right and we love the Lord.

00:18:18.933 --> 00:18:32.194
It's all about having a relationship with the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:18:32.194 --> 00:19:09.200
Those who seek Him will find Him, and that's what we're all trying to do on this channel.

00:19:09.200 --> 00:19:32.491
Our number one goal is just to smile at Jesus today.

00:19:44.106 --> 00:19:49.006
It's not about race, gender, or money; we look at Jesus.

00:19:49.006 --> 00:20:14.960
I'm excited that we break down those walls; we're just one big happy family in the body of Christ.

00:20:14.960 --> 00:20:44.700
We can have doctrinal differences, but we can agree to disagree and love each other.

00:20:44.700 --> 00:21:00.650
It's like a family reunion—you might not agree with everything, but you still give them a hug.

00:21:00.650 --> 00:21:13.920
Politics is a big one, but we are family and we still love each other.

00:21:27.820 --> 00:21:30.990
I felt in my spirit that the Holy Spirit said to address that.

00:21:30.990 --> 00:21:45.337
Father, we take authority over any kind of demonic attack over Nevada and Las Vegas.

00:23:58.910 --> 00:24:46.503
We pray that all hidden things be revealed and that there will be no plots, calamities, shootings, or bombings in any hotel or casino.

00:27:50.133 --> 00:28:20.530
I plead the blood of Jesus over the Strip.

00:28:20.530 --> 00:29:00.570
Where sin abounds, grace does much more abound.

00:29:00.570 --> 00:29:54.543
We call forth all these things to be revealed—anything the devil has tried to stir up.

00:29:54.543 --> 00:33:30.891
We wrestle not against flesh and blood, but against principalities and powers.

00:33:45.413 --> 00:37:20.950
I just saw in a vision to pray over the Macy's Thanksgiving Day Parade.

00:37:20.960 --> 00:38:26.790
I pray a hedge of protection around those people in New York and call for an uncovering of darkness.

00:38:26.800 --> 00:39:04.968
I thank You that the NYPD, FBI, and CIA would have supernatural thinking to check things they might not otherwise check.

00:39:25.022 --> 00:39:35.031
I pray for a covering over families during the Christmas season and over the shopping malls.

00:39:35.031 --> 00:39:47.920
I pray for a special hedge of protection over Atlanta, Georgia.

00:39:47.920 --> 00:41:09.943
As people travel on American, United, Southwest, and other flights, I call for protection during this busiest traveling time.

00:41:09.943 --> 00:41:32.583
We call for any terrorist activity to be uncovered and found out right now.

00:41:32.583 --> 00:42:14.675
When I start hitting something in the spirit realm, I feel my spirit tugging on it like a metal detector.

00:42:14.675 --> 00:42:47.344
There's something about the planes and something around Atlanta, so we're going to pray over travels.

00:42:47.344 --> 00:43:41.013
We pray over the Ukraine situation; we call for peace and not an acceleration of war.

00:43:41.013 --> 00:43:58.471
We call for a delay in the Antichrist agenda so that we will have our revival.

00:43:58.471 --> 00:44:04.090
It's about a one-world system; I see the spirit that's driving them.

00:44:06.816 --> 00:44:13.009
I call for a delay concerning this war in Jesus' name.

00:44:13.009 --> 00:44:36.560
You pulled the slack out of Pharaoh, and You can pull the slack out of these men.

00:44:36.560 --> 00:44:52.400
Assyria is referred to as the land of Nimrod.

00:45:01.760 --> 00:45:14.773
I see a deflating and a delaying of it for the harvest.

00:45:34.607 --> 00:45:39.209
I see a window of four years settled in the courts of the throne.

00:45:39.209 --> 00:46:06.019
The enemy would try to tip it over, but we rise up and take back the time.

00:46:06.019 --> 00:46:21.200
I see a fountain of great wealth—beauty and gold—like the glory.

00:46:26.800 --> 00:46:53.920
It's like kicking the can down the road, moving the years 2028, 2029, and 2030 to give time for a revival.

00:47:00.580 --> 00:47:24.560
I see Trump stepping in and not allowing a third world war to happen in these 60 days.

00:47:24.560 --> 00:47:47.664
'Many hands make light work'—the Lord just quoted that to me from the principle in Nehemiah chapter 3.

00:47:47.664 --> 00:48:18.062
It seemed so big because of what it takes to spin it in the spirit realm with Putin, Europe, and Emmanuel Macron.

00:48:18.338 --> 00:48:48.880
The United States was trying to play like a puppet master, but they are the most guilty because they were funding it.

00:48:48.880 --> 00:49:10.984
If you cut off the drug dealer and the bank cartel funneling the money, you solve the problem.

00:49:14.685 --> 00:49:28.491
I saw great wealth coming out of the Trump administration as it turns.

00:49:28.491 --> 00:49:34.820
I call forth Elon Musk to be saved and have a visitation from the Lord.

00:49:34.820 --> 00:50:10.160
I call for the blinders to be removed from his eyes so he would know the hope of his calling.

00:50:12.880 --> 00:50:33.680
I bind the enemy and call him free to make his own decision concerning the Gospel.

00:50:51.824 --> 00:51:04.679
I thank You that he would use Starlink for the glory of God to bring in the Great Harvest.

00:51:09.320 --> 00:51:20.800
I pray for divine intervention for Hollywood celebrities to influence the world with light, not darkness.

00:51:20.800 --> 00:51:40.559
We call Taylor Swift to be born again and have a visitation from Jesus.

00:51:52.142 --> 00:52:18.979
I pray for a stirring in Kanye West again, that he would be radically born again and surrounded by godly influencers.

00:52:18.979 --> 00:52:21.669
We rise up like David taking the head off the giant.

00:52:53.200 --> 00:52:58.400
I speak to the SEC to leave certain cryptos alone and for the lawsuits to stop.

00:53:04.720 --> 00:53:17.234
I command this demonic spirit trying to hinder the wealth transfer to desist.

00:53:17.234 --> 00:53:36.760
We call for a great wealth transfer for the glory of God.

00:53:45.200 --> 00:53:53.821
We are strong together when we move as a body, like an ant colony.

00:53:53.821 --> 00:54:15.887
Please subscribe and click the notification bell; it helps get the Gospel spread throughout the whole world.

00:54:21.429 --> 00:54:31.808
God bless you all, and we will see you again tomorrow.
